{
  "info": {
    "name": "Marketplace API â€” Payment",
    "_postman_id": "marketplace-api-v2-07-payment",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{access_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url",    "value": "http://localhost:8000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "access_token","value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refresh_token","value": "",                     "type": "string" },
    { "key": "order_id",    "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "payment_id",  "value": "",                      "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "07. Payment",
      "description": "Initiate & manage payments via Xendit / Midtrans gateway",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Initiate Payment đź”’",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('payment_id', String(body.data.id || ''));",
                  "  pm.test('Initiate payment returns 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "  pm.test('Response has payment data', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('id');",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('status');",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('amount_cents');",
                  "  });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept",            "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",      "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Idempotency-Key", "value": "{{$guid}}", "description": "Unique key per request â€” prevents double payment" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"order_id\": {{order_id}},\n  \"gateway\": \"xendit\",\n  \"method\": \"virtual_account\",\n  \"bank_code\": \"BCA\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/payments/initiate",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "payments", "initiate"]
            },
            "description": "Buat gateway charge dan Payment record.\n\n**Selalu sertakan `X-Idempotency-Key`** (UUID) untuk mencegah double charge.\n\n**method** options:\n- `virtual_account` â†’ `bank_code` required (BCA/BNI/BRI/MANDIRI)\n- `qris` â†’ universal QRIS, no extra params\n- `ewallet` â†’ `ewallet_type` required (OVO/DANA/GOPAY/SHOPEEPAY/LINKAJA); OVO also needs `phone`\n- `invoice` â†’ Xendit hosted checkout (legacy)\n- `snap` â†’ Midtrans Snap hosted checkout (use `gateway: midtrans`)\n\n`amount` stored as integer cents."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "201 Created â€” Virtual Account",
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Payment initiated successfully.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"order_id\": 5,\n    \"gateway\": \"xendit\",\n    \"method\": \"virtual_account\",\n    \"amount_cents\": 39000000,\n    \"amount\": \"Rp 390.000\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"payment_details\": {\n      \"bank_code\": \"BCA\",\n      \"account_number\": \"8808123456789\",\n      \"virtual_account_id\": \"va-xxx\"\n    },\n    \"redirect_url\": null,\n    \"expires_at\": \"2026-05-13T10:00:00.000000Z\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "201 Created â€” QRIS",
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Payment initiated successfully.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 2,\n    \"order_id\": 6,\n    \"gateway\": \"xendit\",\n    \"method\": \"qris\",\n    \"amount_cents\": 50000000,\n    \"amount\": \"Rp 500.000\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"payment_details\": {\n      \"qr_id\": \"qr-xxx\",\n      \"qr_string\": \"00020101021226...\"\n    },\n    \"redirect_url\": null,\n    \"expires_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:05:00.000000Z\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "201 Created â€” GoPay E-wallet",
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Payment initiated successfully.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 3,\n    \"order_id\": 7,\n    \"gateway\": \"xendit\",\n    \"method\": \"ewallet\",\n    \"amount_cents\": 100000000,\n    \"amount\": \"Rp 1.000.000\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"payment_details\": {\n      \"ewallet_type\": \"GOPAY\",\n      \"charge_id\": \"ewc-xxx\",\n      \"checkout_url\": \"https://wallet.google.com/gopay/...\"\n    },\n    \"redirect_url\": \"https://wallet.google.com/gopay/...\",\n    \"expires_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:05:00.000000Z\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "422 Unprocessable â€” Missing ewallet_type",
              "status": "Unprocessable Entity",
              "code": 422,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"The given data was invalid.\",\n  \"errors\": {\n    \"ewallet_type\": [\"The ewallet type field is required when method is ewallet.\"]\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Payment Status đź”’",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Get status returns 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Response has status field', () => {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('status');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/payments/{{payment_id}}/status",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "payments", "{{payment_id}}", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Poll status pembayaran. Frontend menggunakan ini untuk mendeteksi saat pembayaran VA/QRIS selesai.\n\nReturns Payment dengan relasi order dan transaction."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Payment status retrieved.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"order_id\": 5,\n    \"gateway\": \"xendit\",\n    \"method\": \"virtual_account\",\n    \"amount_cents\": 39000000,\n    \"amount\": \"Rp 390.000\",\n    \"status\": \"paid\",\n    \"payment_details\": { \"bank_code\": \"BCA\", \"account_number\": \"8808123456789\" },\n    \"redirect_url\": null,\n    \"expires_at\": \"2026-05-13T10:00:00.000000Z\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Request Refund đź”’",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Refund returns 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Refund has id', () => {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('id');",
                  "  pm.expect(body.data.status).to.equal('processed');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept",       "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"Item not received\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/payments/{{payment_id}}/refund",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "payments", "{{payment_id}}", "refund"]
            },
            "description": "Request refund untuk payment milik user yang terautentikasi.\n\n- **Paid**: gateway refundPayment() + create Refund record + Payment status â†’ refunded\n- **Pending/Expired**: cancel only â€” no gateway call, Payment status â†’ failed\n\nHanya buyer pemilik order yang dapat request refund."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Refund processed successfully.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"payment_id\": 1,\n    \"amount_cents\": 39000000,\n    \"amount\": \"Rp 390.000\",\n    \"reason\": \"Item not received\",\n    \"status\": \"processed\",\n    \"refunded_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "404 Not Found â€” Wrong User",
              "status": "Not Found",
              "code": 404,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"No query results for model [App\\\\Models\\\\Payment].\",\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "07. Wallet",
      "description": "Wallet balance, transactions, top-up and merchant withdrawal",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Wallet Balance đź”’",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Balance returns 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Response has balance fields', () => {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('balance_cents');",
                  "  pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('available_cents');",
                  "  pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('on_hold_cents');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/wallet/balance",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "wallet", "balance"]
            },
            "description": "Ambil saldo wallet user yang terautentikasi.\n\nWallet dibuat otomatis (`firstOrCreate`) saat pertama kali diakses â€” tidak perlu inisialisasi manual.\n\n`available_cents = balance_cents - on_hold_cents`"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Wallet balance retrieved.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"balance_cents\": 50000000,\n    \"balance\": \"Rp 500.000\",\n    \"on_hold_cents\": 10000000,\n    \"on_hold\": \"Rp 100.000\",\n    \"available_cents\": 40000000,\n    \"available\": \"Rp 400.000\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "List Wallet Transactions đź”’",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Transactions returns 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Response has pagination', () => {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(body.meta).to.have.property('pagination');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/wallet/transactions?page=1",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "wallet", "transactions"],
              "query": [{ "key": "page", "value": "1" }]
            },
            "description": "Riwayat transaksi wallet user (paginated, 20 per page, latest first).\n\n`type`: `credit` (masuk) atau `debit` (keluar)"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Wallet transactions retrieved.\",\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 2,\n      \"type\": \"credit\",\n      \"amount_cents\": 50000000,\n      \"amount\": \"Rp 500.000\",\n      \"description\": \"Top-up via BCA VA\",\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"type\": \"debit\",\n      \"amount_cents\": 10000000,\n      \"amount\": \"Rp 100.000\",\n      \"description\": \"Withdrawal â€” on_hold\",\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-05-12T09:00:00.000000Z\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\",\n    \"pagination\": { \"current_page\": 1, \"last_page\": 1, \"per_page\": 20, \"total\": 2 }\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Topup Wallet đź”’",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept",       "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"amount\": 50000000\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/wallet/topup",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "wallet", "topup"]
            },
            "description": "Initiate wallet top-up via payment gateway.\n\nAlur: POST ini mengembalikan instruksi untuk melanjutkan ke `POST /api/payments/initiate` dengan jumlah yang sama. Kredit wallet terjadi otomatis via `PaymentCaptured` â†’ `CreditUserWallet` listener setelah pembayaran berhasil.\n\n`amount` dalam integer cents. Min: Rp 10.000 (1000000 cents)."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Top-up payment initiated. Complete payment to credit wallet.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"message\": \"Redirect user to initiate a payment via POST /api/payments/initiate with the wallet top-up amount.\",\n    \"amount\": 50000000\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Withdraw (Merchant Only) đź”’",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Withdraw returns 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('on_hold increased', () => {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(body.data.on_hold_cents).to.be.greaterThan(0);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept",       "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"amount\": 10000000,\n  \"bank_code\": \"BCA\",\n  \"account_number\": \"1234567890\",\n  \"account_name\": \"Merchant Demo\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/wallet/withdraw",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "wallet", "withdraw"]
            },
            "description": "Merchant meminta pencairan saldo wallet ke rekening bank.\n\n**Hanya untuk akun Merchant (role=merchant)**. Buyer mendapat 403.\n\nAlur `on_hold`:\n1. Withdraw request â†’ `balance -= amount`, `on_hold += amount`\n2. Disbursement webhook SUCCESS â†’ `on_hold -= amount` (permanently deducted)\n3. Disbursement webhook FAILED â†’ `on_hold -= amount`, `balance += amount` (rollback)\n\n`amount` dalam integer cents. Tidak boleh melebihi `available_cents`."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Withdrawal initiated. Funds will be transferred within 1-3 business days.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"balance_cents\": 40000000,\n    \"balance\": \"Rp 400.000\",\n    \"on_hold_cents\": 10000000,\n    \"on_hold\": \"Rp 100.000\",\n    \"available_cents\": 30000000,\n    \"available\": \"Rp 300.000\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "422 Unprocessable â€” Insufficient Balance",
              "status": "Unprocessable Entity",
              "code": 422,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Insufficient balance.\",\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "403 Forbidden â€” Not Merchant",
              "status": "Forbidden",
              "code": 403,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"This action is unauthorized.\",\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
